  "text": "To get more quantitative information on the resulting average volumetric mass density of the two layers, XRR and RBS experiments were performed. X-ray reflectivity curves are shown in Figure 2 . We reported also on the plot, as an indicative guideline, a simulation for bulk graphite with a volumetric mass density, , of 2.28 g/cm [CITATION_1] . The low incident angle part corresponds to the total reflection regime. The reflectivity rapidly falls at the critical angle, .",
